 
<p>

  US citizens: call on Congress to <a href="https://actionnetwork.org/forms/sign-the-petition-congress-must-repeal-the-comstock-act">repeal the Comstock Act</a>.
<p>
That disused law prohibits mailing "lewd" or "obscene" materials
through the post, and also prohibits mailing birth control and
abortifacients.  Republicans want to enforce it <a href="https://stallman.org/archives/2023-jan-apr.html#16_April_2023_(The_Supreme_Court_intervened_on_mifepristone)">against mailing of
    mifepristone</a>.

The Capitol Switchboard numbers are
<a href="tel:+12022243121">+1-202-224-3121</a>,
<a href="tel:+18888186641">+1-888-818-6641</a> and
<a href="tel:+18883553588">+1-888-355-3588</a>.
<p>
If you phone, please spread the word!<p>

 